rules.cssText: #header { background: url("chrome://firebug/content/firefox/images/bg-top-bot.png") repeat-x scroll 0px -130px rgb(0, 178, 0); height: 80px; width: 100%; padding-top: 10px; border-bottom: 14px solid rgb(203, 201, 196); }
#centralContainer { width: 1040px; height: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

.mapContainer { border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; padding: 5px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 6px 3px gray; color: rgb(0, 80, 124); width: 470px; height: 270px; margin: 10px; background-image: url("chrome://firebug/content/firefox/images/Si_Map_Part.png"); }
.marking { width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px; float: left; margin-left: -7px; }
.label { float: left; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 205); padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 10px; box-shadow: -1px 0px 1px 2px rgb(255, 250, 205); }

.styledSelectContainer select { background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% transparent; width: 268px; padding: 5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; border: 0px none; border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px; height: 34px; cursor: pointer; }

.styledSelectContainer { width: 200px; height: 34px; overflow: hidden; background: url("chrome://firebug/content/firefox/images/down_arrow_select.jpg") no-repeat scroll right center rgb(221, 221, 221); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); margin: 9px 9px 15px; cursor: pointer; }
.imagesContainer { border-style: solid; border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px 2px gray; border-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); margin-top: 15px; }

#imageSelectorContainer a { background-image: url("chrome://firebug/content/firefox/images/billboard-pager.png"); width: 20px; height: 20px; display: block; outline: medium none; text-decoration: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; }
.linkContainer { background: url("chrome://firebug/content/firefox/images/root-background_left.gif") no-repeat scroll 0px 0px transparent; margin-top: 10px; padding: 5px; }

.menuItem { background-color: rgb(0, 142, 0); color: white; border-style: solid; border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px 2px gray; padding: 5px; min-width: 50px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; }

childNodes.textContent: Set amid the wild beauty of white karstic rock and the azure sea, the Šibenik aquatorium is a yachting paradise, boasting as many as 240 isles and reefs, each of which holds an interesting feature or two. If you want to meet the best known coral hunters in the Adriatic, set sail for Zlarin. If you wish to see the centre of sea sponge harvesting, then Krapanj is your destination. On the other hand, if you seek an experience like no other, then venture into the open sea and discover the Kornati Archipelago.
